621
00:22:19,638 --> 00:22:22,374
NEWBIE'S JOURNEY OF FOLLOWING
THOSE MANY CLUB MEMBERS

622
00:22:23,875 --> 00:22:26,578
HAS COME TO AN END

623
00:22:26,645 --> 00:22:28,747
WHICH CLUB WOULD YOU LIKE TO SETTLE ON?

624
00:22:28,814 --> 00:22:30,148
I like all of them,

625
00:22:31,583 --> 00:22:32,984
but tennis was kind of fun.

626
00:22:35,454 --> 00:22:36,621
Dragon boating too.

627
00:22:37,789 --> 00:22:39,791
All the other clubs were very fun too,

628
00:22:39,858 --> 00:22:43,195
but the most memorable ones
are the ones I've done recently.

629
00:22:44,062 --> 00:22:45,063
HOW WAS YOUR JOURNEY AS NEWBIE?

630
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:49,301
When I was observing and participating
in all the club activities,

631
00:22:49,368 --> 00:22:52,571
I realized that there are so many who live

632
00:22:52,637 --> 00:22:56,475
such great, energetic
and cool lives in Korea.

633
00:22:56,541 --> 00:22:58,377
There were so many fields
I didn't know about,

634
00:22:58,443 --> 00:22:59,878
so I enjoyed learning about them.

635
00:22:59,945 --> 00:23:03,048
Most importantly,
I really realized that it is

636
00:23:03,115 --> 00:23:05,317
so much fun
to do things with other people.

